    "longBusinessSummary": "Digiworld Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, operates as a market expansion services provider in Vietnam. The company trades in technological software products, computers and accessories, and electronic accessories; telephones, switchboards, and air conditioners; consumer products; and laptops, mobile phones, office equipment, and enterprise solutions. It is also involved in the transfer of information technology and automatic controls; and provision of goods consignment agency services, as well as management and consulting services, and trading labor protection solutions. In addition, the company engages in pharmaceutical distribution; pawnshop services; audio-visual equipment and home appliance repair; software production; and real estate activities. Further, it provides sales and marketing services comprising distribution channel solutions, trade execution, and brand strategy; e-commerce distribution solutions comprising the creation and management of e-commerce stores, management of webpage/fanpage, online marketing, and e-logistics and fulfilment; research and business planning services; full distribution solutions consisting of importation, warehouse services, and distribution; after-sales services; and store management services, such as selection of location, construction and designing of store, recruitment and training of employees, and operation of stores. Digiworld Corporation was founded in 1997 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
